comments: White (CHI) initiates contact with Jones' (NOP) left arm at the start of the drive and affects his SQBR.
Murphy III (NOP) brings his hands toward Dosunmu (CHI) as he sets the pick and marginal contact occurs before Dosunmu briefly stumbles over Ingram's leg.
Murphy III (NOP) moves alongside DeRozan's (CHI) path and marginal body contact occurs during the driving shot attempt.
DeRozan (CHI) and Williamson (NOP) pursue the loose ball and marginal arm contact occurs during the rebound.
Caruso (CHI) delivers contact to Ingram (NOP) and dislodges him from his position.
Vucevic (CHI) is attempting to establish himself in Jones' (NOP) path and marginal contact occurs as Jones moves around the screen.
Jones (NOP) close-out toward White's (CHI) jump shot attempt and marginal foot to foot contact occurs after White returns to the floor.
Valanciunas (NOP) establishes himself in DeRozan's (CHI) path with his legs within the frame of his body as contact occurs, which he does not deliver.
White (CHI) and Valanciunas (NOP) pursue the loose ball and marginal arm contact occurs during the rebound.
Caruso (CHI) reaches for the ball and marginal contact occurs with Valanciunas' (NOP) right arm during his finish at the rim.

Williamson (NOP) blocks Vucevic's (CHI) shot attempt and on the follow though, makes marginal contact with Vucevic's head.  Contact to an opponent's head/face can be deemed marginal when the result of a natural basketball move, provided the contact is not disproportionate or uncontrolled.
Jones (NOP) commits a take foul on DeRozan (CHI).

call_type: Turnover: Lost Ball Out of Bounds
comments: The ball goes OOB off Ingram's (NOP) hands.
Hawkins (NOP) commits a take foul on White (CHI).
